I had pain in my wisdom tooth due to decay, but I was skeptical to visit a dentist due to the current Covid-19 pandemic. However, When I visited Dr. Surana's clinic, to my relief I observed that they were taking all the precautionary measures like regularly sanitising the clinic, checking patient's temperature and oxygen levels, wearing PPE kits etc. Dr Surana explained to me in detail about my condition and how it could be fixed. Having OCD I tend to ask too many questions, however, Dr. Surana heard all my doubts patiently and cleared them all. My treatment was carried out extremely safely and now I'm pain free. I would definitely recommend Dr Surana to everyone.

Dr. Nikhil Surana was extremely courteous & welcoming. He carefully listened to my problem and gave the right advice to extract my decaying tooth. He did a splendid job at that.
